---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab CEO Discusses SAP.iO on Industry Insights Podcast - parcelLab"
  description="CEO Tobias Buxhoidt discusses parcelLab's experience with the SAP.iO program and how the platform helps brands manage post-purchase communications."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab CEO Discusses SAP.iO on Industry Insights Podcast</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2021-04-08">April 8, 2021</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          CEO Tobias Buxhoidt participated in an SAP Industry Insights podcast interview with host Josephine Monberg. The discussion included Max Kissel, founder of Soley and fellow SAP.iO program participant, exploring how the program has accelerated growth for both companies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Our Innovative Solution</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab's platform enables brands to manage communications across operational processes including delivery, shipping, and returns. Rather than relying on carrier-generated emails, the system provides brands with complete control over end-to-end customer communication.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">CEO Perspective</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Whenever products are being shipped, it is important to be there for the customer and offer a good service. That's where we come in. It's not just about shipping stuff anymore. It's about what digital services you can create around it."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Tobias Buxhoidt, CEO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Value of SAP.iO</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The SAP.iO program provided parcelLab with valuable exposure and customer access, helping accelerate growth and establish enterprise relationships.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">On SAP.iO</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"We're very happy that we're doing this with SAP. Specifically, the .iO program has helped us a lot... gaining visibility, getting in front of customers."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Tobias Buxhoidt, CEO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The full podcast episode is available through SAP's Industry Insights podcast platform, providing additional context on parcelLab's platform capabilities and how brands can transform their post-purchase operations into competitive advantages.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
